Entity Note

Event create_note
  NewEntry  Action perform_note_creation

Event update_note
  When status = Active    Action perform_note_update
  When status = Archived  Action reject_request

Event archive_note
  When status = Active    Action perform_note_archive
  When status = Archived  Action notify_already_archived

Event create_automatic_note
  NewEntry  Action perform_automatic_note_creation
